Fault Domain: Fault Domain = Protection from unexpected hardware failures.
-- Handles hardware failures
-- Different racks/power/network
-- Protects against server or rack crash

Update Domain:  Purpose: Protects against planned maintenance/reboots.
-- Handles maintenance failures
-- Different reboot groups
-- Protects against Azure patching and upgrades

Fault Domain = Physical isolation for hardware failure protection.
Update Domain = Logical isolation for maintenance and reboot protection.

